<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٥٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٩٣٥٥ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قال:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ: قَالَ ابْنُ شِهَابٍ: فِي رَجُلٍ مِنْ أَهْلِ الْكِتَابِ اشْتَرَى أَمَةً مُسْلِمَةً سِرًّا , فَوَلَدَتْ لَهُ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُغَرَّبُ وَتُنْتَزَعُ مِنْهُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>